Name: NABOKI
About the game: NABOKI is a minimal puzzle game about taking levels apart. Just like my previous games, there are no tutorials, no scores and no text. Just a simple, relaxing, peaceful puzzle experience. Calm gameplay is accompanied by ambient, meditative soundtrack created by Wojciech Wasiak.
